This is my Ruby-based wmii configuration, explained in these articles:

  http://snk.tuxfamily.org/lib/rumai/

  http://snk.tuxfamily.org/web/2006-07-01-wmii-3-1-configuration-in-ruby.html

Dependencies:

    git clone git://github.com/sunaku/rumai.git ~/wmii-3.5/rumai

    gem install librmpd

Installation:

    mv ~/.wmii-3.5 ~/.wmii-3.5.backup

    git clone git://github.com/Tass/wmiirc.git ~/.wmii-3.5

    chmod +x ~/.wmii-3.5/wmiirc

    ~/.wmii-3.5/wmiirc

